{
  "_comment": [
    "浏览器大脑 (Browser Brain) 配置示例",
    "Browser Brain 是 sidecar 架构，由 Kernel 通过 stdio JSON-RPC 启动",
    "本文件内容合并写入 ~/.brain/config.json 即可生效",
    "",
    "环境变量：",
    "  BROWSER_PATH           指定浏览器可执行文件路径（默认自动检测）",
    "  BRAIN_CONFIG           覆盖默认配置文件路径（默认 ~/.brain/config.json）",
    "  BRAIN_LICENSE_REQUIRED 设为 1 强制要求 license 校验",
    "",
    "浏览器自动检测顺序（Linux）：",
    "  1. google-chrome-stable / google-chrome",
    "  2. chromium-browser / chromium",
    "  3. microsoft-edge-stable",
    "  4. brave-browser-stable",
    "",
    "浏览器启动参数（内置不可修改）：",
    "  --headless=new  --window-size=1920,1080  --no-sandbox  --disable-gpu",
    "",
    "注册工具（15 个）：",
    "  browser.open / navigate / click / double_click / right_click",
    "  browser.type / press_key / scroll / hover / drag",
    "  browser.select / upload_file / screenshot / eval / wait",
    "",
    "执行预算（通过 RPC ExecuteRequest 传入）：",
    "  budget.max_turns: 15（默认）"
  ],

  "tool_profiles": {
    "browser_safe": {
      "include": ["browser.*"],
      "exclude": ["browser.eval"]
    },
    "browser_full": {
      "include": ["browser.*"],
      "exclude": []
    }
  },

  "active_tools": {
    "delegate.browser": "browser_safe"
  },

  "file_policy": {
    "allow_read": ["**/*.html", "**/*.png", "**/*.jpg"],
    "allow_create": ["screenshots/**"],
    "allow_edit": [],
    "allow_delete": [],
    "deny": [".git/**", "**/.env"]
  }
}
